ascend_skill.desc:
(SB)Some skills and Highlight can activate Ice Technicals. When dealing Ice damage, ignore foes' Ice resistance.
On Natsukawa's action, gain 1 Extinguish stack. Stacks up to 4 times. When using Extinguishing Guidance, spend Extinguish stacks, and inflict 1 Damnation stack on all foes for each stack spent.
Damnation: Increase damage taken by 6% for 2 turns. Stacks up to 4 times.
ascend_skill.name: Smothering Agony

ascend_skill.desc: When using Sub-Zero Torrent, gain 1 more Extinguish stack. When spending Extinguish stacks, increase all foes' critical damage taken by 30% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Cooling Spray

ascend_skill.desc: When spending Extinguish stacks, increase party's Attack by 20%, Defense by 30%, and damage dealt by 15% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Frozen Gateway

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Extinguishing Guidance and Thief Tactics by 3.
ascend_skill.name: Whirlpool Cannon

ascend_skill.desc: (SB)Highlight Enhanced: Extend the duration of the damage taken increase effect by 1 turn. Also, when the Highlight activates Deepfreeze, the chance to inflict Icebound becomes 44%.
ascend_skill.name: Terrifying Chill

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Sub-Zero Torrent and Freezing Prison by 3.
ascend_skill.name: Wellspring of Grief

ascend_skill.desc:
When foes are Burning on Natsukawa's action, activate Sub-Zero Torrent on that foe 1 time (this effect will not be activated by Scald).
Also, when the same foe is attacked repeatedly with Extinguishing Guidance or Requiem Guidance, increase the target's damage taken by 25% more for 1 turn.
The maximum number of Damnation stacks becomes 6.
ascend_skill.name: Firefighter's Soul

highlight_skill.desc:
(SB)Deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 39.0%/43.0%/41.4%/45.4%, and increase their damage taken for 2 turns (for every 5.83% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, increase damage taken by 1%, up to a maximum of 29.3%/32.3%/31.1%/34.1%).
At the same time, if an Ice Technical can be activated, when Deepfreeze is activated, 32% chance to inflict Icebound. Also, increase damage taken by enemies inflicted with Freeze by this Highlight (for every 17.5% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, increase damage taken by 1%, up to a maximum of 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4%).
Then, deal additional Ice damage to all foes equal to 117.1%/129.1%/124.3%/136.3% of Attack.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
(SB)Gain 1 Extinguish stack, and deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 97.6%/107.6%/103.6%/113.6% of Attack. 50% chance to inflict Freeze.
Also, decrease Defense by 7.8%/8.6%/8.3%/9.1% for 3 turns (for every 5.47% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, decrease Defense by 1%, up to 31.2%/34.4%/33.2%/36.4%). When an ally attacks a foe with Defense decreased by this skill, increase Technical Precision by 195/195/207/207.
If the target is inflicted with Burn, remove Burn and inflict Scald (cannot be inflicted if Scald is already active).
Scald: Counts as Burn. Lasts for 3 turns. When allies attack the affected foe, increase Technical Precision by 1186/1308/1259/1381.
normal_skill.name: Sub-Zero Torrent

normal_skill.desc: Deal Ice damage to 1 foe equal to 195.2%/215.2%/207.2%/227.2%, and activate an Ice Technical. When Deepfreeze is activated, 48.0%/52.9%/51.0%/55.9% chance to inflict Icebound.
normal_skill.name: Freezing Prison

normal_skill.desc:
Can be used at 2 or more Extinguish stacks. Spend 2 Extinguish stacks. Deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 109.8%/121.0%/116.6%/127.8% of Attack. Also, decrease Defense by 7.3%/8.1%/7.8%/8.5% for 2 turns (for every 5.83% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, decrease Defense by 1%, up to a maximum of 29.3%/32.3%/31.1%/34.1%).
Also, an Ice Technical can be activated. When Iceburn is activated, this effect is guaranteed to inflict Cold Flames.
Cold Flames: Increase damage taken by 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% (for every 4.38% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, increase damage taken by 1%, up to a maximum of 39.0%/43.0%/41.4%/45.4%).
At 4 or more stacks, can strengthen Requiem Guidance.
Spend 4 Extinguish stacks. Deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 131.8%/145.3%/139.9%/153.4% of Attack. Also, decrease Defense by 8.8%/9.7%/9.3%/10.2% for 2 turns (for every 4.86% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, decrease Defense by 1%, up to a maximum of 35.1%/38.7%/37.3%/40.9%).
At the same time, an Ice Technical can be activated. When Iceburn is activated, this effect is guaranteed to inflict Cold Flames.
Cold Flames: Increase damage taken by 11.7%/12.9%/12.4%/13.6% (for every 3.65% of Natsukawa's ailment accuracy, increase damage taken by 1%, up to a maximum of 46.8%/51.6%/49.7%/54.5%).
normal_skill.name: Extinguishing Guidance

passive_skill.desc: Each time Natsukawa activates a Technical, grant all allies a shield that protects against 1050 damage for 2 turns.
passive_skill.name: Disaster Preparedness

passive_skill.desc: (SB)When Natsukawa is present, increase Frozen foes' damage taken by 27.0%, and increase damage taken by foes with Icebound by 27.0%.
passive_skill.name: Biting Cold
